{ Hi guys!! Welcome back! Today, your goal is to steal EVERYTHING in the house. Once you do that, you need to escape the house and not get caught. All before that, you need to steal the key to enter the house, and make sure not to get caught!

Please leave a like! Have fun and steal everything.

You have a total of 3 lives. 1 hint means that you lose 1. A mistake means that you lose 1 too. You use puzzles to finish your goal of stealing all the items in the house.

Credit to @DrCookieZ for making two of these kinds of studies and inspiring me to do this! }
 *


