{ To get the key, you need to solve this puzzle! }
1... Qg3!! { 1,000,000 GOLDEN COINS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! } 2. Qxg3 Ne2+ 3. Kh1 Nxg3+ 4. fxg3 Rxf1# { You have now gotten the key! Now it is time to enter the house. } *


