{ Solve this puzzle to enter the house! }
1. Nf6+ Kg7 2. Nh5+ Kg6 3. Bc2+ Kxh5 4. d8=Q Nf7+ 5. Ke6 Nxd8+ 6. Kf5 e2 7. Be4 e1=N 8. Bd5 c2 9. Bc4 c1=N 10. Bb5 Nc6 11. Bxc6 Nc7 12. Ba4 Ne2 13. Bd1 Nf3 14. Bxe2 Be1 15. Bxf3# { You have finished the puzzle! Now it is time to steal the items in the first floor. } *


